394
00:18:35.865 --> 00:18:38.118
Zero to sixty in 3.1 seconds.

395
00:18:38.201 --> 00:18:41.037
- I guess that's good.
- TECH: Watch this.

396
00:18:41.121 --> 00:18:43.540
Car. open doors.

397
00:18:43.623 --> 00:18:44.999
(GRUNTS)

398
00:18:46.126 --> 00:18:48.044
