402
00:18:52.841 --> 00:18:54.259
- (GENTLE CHIME)
- (ED GROANING)

403
00:18:54.342 --> 00:18:56.136
- (FINGERS CRUNCH)
- (STRAINED SCREAM)

404
00:18:56.928 --> 00:18:58.096
Hey!

405
00:18:58.179 --> 00:18:59.305
Pretty fun. I guess.

406
00:18:59.389 --> 00:19:00.974
Okay. how about this? Car...

407
00:19:01.057 --> 00:19:03.434
drive forward 30 feet.

408
00:19:04.144 --> 00:19:05.311
(FRANK CHUCKLES)

409
00:19:06.938 --> 00:19:08.022
