438
00:20:31.147 --> 00:20:33.066
(SCATTING ABSENTMINDEDLY)

439
00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:38.112
<i>Dispatch. this is Drebin. 10-7.</i>

440
00:20:38.196 --> 00:20:39.489
