444
00:20:44.869 --> 00:20:46.537
Breakfast of champions.

445
00:20:46.621 --> 00:20:47.747
FRANK: <i>And a little black coffee.</i>

446
00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:50.083
Okay. you can fast-forward a bit.

447
00:20:50.833 --> 00:20:52.252
(FAST-FORWARDING)

448
00:20:52.919 --> 00:20:54.629
FRANK: <i>License
and registration. please.</i>

449
00:20:54.712 --> 00:20:56.256
MAN: <i>Uh</i>... (CLEARS THROAT)

450
00:20:57.465 --> 00:20:58.466
<i>Uh</i>... (CHUCKLES)

451
00:20:58.549 --> 00:20:59.550
<i>This isn't mine.</i>

452
00:20:59.634 --> 00:21:00.843
- (WET FLATULENCE)
- FRANK: <i>Excuse me.</i>

453
00:21:01.678 --> 00:21:03.513
- (FARTING CONTINUES)
- FRANK: <i>Oh. boy. Listen. uh.</i>

454
00:21:03.596 --> 00:21:04.889
<i>you seem like a decent fella.</i>

455
00:21:04.973 --> 00:21:07.225
<i>I'm gonna let you off with a warning.
Have a great day. bye.</i>

456
00:21:07.892 --> 00:21:10.603
It's much later in the day.
Fast-forward a while.

457
00:21:10.687 --> 00:21:12.105
(FAST-FORWARDING)

458
00:21:12.188 --> 00:21:13.856
You'll see. Just wait.

459
00:21:13.940 --> 00:21:15.441
