460
00:21:15.525 --> 00:21:17.902
<i>I need a bathroom. Oh. God.</i>

461
00:21:17.986 --> 00:21:19.737
<i>Come on. move. move. move!</i>

462
00:21:20.363 --> 00:21:21.948
