465
00:21:27.662 --> 00:21:28.663
(GRUNTS)

466
00:21:28.746 --> 00:21:29.789
Maybe a little more.

467
00:21:29.872 --> 00:21:31.457
<i>I'm gonna ruin another suit!</i>

468
00:21:31.541 --> 00:21:33.334
- Barnes!
- (PANICKED GROANING)

469
00:21:33.418 --> 00:21:34.460
BARNES: Sorry.

470
00:21:34.544 --> 00:21:35.586
(FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING)

471
00:21:35.670 --> 00:21:37.088
FRANK: <i>Police business!</i>

472
00:21:37.171 --> 00:21:39.424
<i>Uh. there is a line. man!</i> (SCREAMS)

473
00:21:39.507 --> 00:21:40.508
(CUSTOMERS SCREAMING)

474
00:21:43.761 --> 00:21:44.762
FRANK: <i>Come on!</i>

475
00:21:45.763 --> 00:21:47.056
(FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING)

476
00:21:48.975 --> 00:21:51.644
<i>You're disgusting. you stupid idiot.</i>

477
00:21:53.062 --> 00:21:55.815
<i>Breastfed until you were 13.
you freak.</i>

478
00:21:55.898 --> 00:21:57.567
(FOOTAGE FAST-FORWARDING)

479
00:21:57.650 --> 00:22:01.154
<i>Can't get it up without
